This paper deals with medical image segmentation using machine learning techniques such as semi-supervised learning and graph cuts. The paper focuses on image analysis and computer vision, which are subfields of computer science. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
